    "desc": "The return of tank design for the Beigee Armory. A fast tank with 3 men in the fighting compartment. The driver sits in the extended driving position while the gunner and loader stand in the round turret. Whenever the loader is not busy with supplying the gun, he will raise his head to the top vision slits which provides 360 degree visibility.",
